title: George and Amal Clooney Step Out to Take Selfies With Fans After Pregnancy Debut
text: George and Amal Clooney Step Out to Take Selfies With Fans After Pregnancy Debut by Jennifer Drysdale 2:59 PM PST, February 25, 2017 Photo: Getty Images Amal Clooney's pregnancy style continues to impress! The 39-year-old attorney looked chic as ever as she stepped out with her husband, George Clooney, in Paris, just one day after her fashionable baby bump debut. Amal, who rocked chic black and white dress and matching coat, kept close to her husband as the two walked around in Paris on Saturday, even stopping to take a few selfies with fans. Photo: Getty Images Photo: Getty Images Photo: Getty Images Amal showed off her baby bump for the first time in a feathered Versace ensemble while accompanying George to the 42nd César Awards in Paris on Friday. The couple is definitely making the most of their time before their twins' spring arrival. George, 55, recently opened up to Recontres de Cinema about becoming a father for the first time, revealing that he and Amal are excited for the "adventure." "We are really happy and really excited," the actor said, beaming. "It's going to be an adventure." "We've sort of embraced it all… with arms wide open," he added.
